Tumblr Tuesday: This one goes out to The Creature
It's a Tuesday in November of the year 2025, and Guillermo Del Toro's Frankenstein has us all in its clutches. The Creature in particular has really captured your collective imaginations as we all relive our love for a 207-year-old taleâ€”and thankfully, the artists on Tumblr have our best interests at heart. Please enjoy this collection of Frankenstein art. Spoilers (and many depictions of The Creature) ahead!
(Tap on the attribution to go to the original post :)
